# Pulih - Psychology Chatbot Flowchart 🌿

## System Architecture Overview

```mermaid
flowchart TB
    subgraph Client["🖥️ Frontend (Browser)"]
        UI[HTML/CSS/JS]
        Auth[Auth Module]
        Chat[Chat Module]
        Mood[Mood Tracker]
        Journal[Journal Module]
        Profile[Profile Module]
    end
    
    subgraph Server["⚙️ Backend (Node.js/Express)"]
        API[Express Router]
        AuthRoute["/api/auth"]
        ChatRoute["/api/chat"]
        MoodRoute["/api/mood"]
        JournalRoute["/api/journal"]
        ProfileRoute["/api/profile"]
        Utils[Utilities]
    end
    
    subgraph External["☁️ External Services"]
        AI[Heroku Inference API]
        DB[(MySQL/JawsDB)]
    end
    
    UI --> API
    Auth --> AuthRoute
    Chat --> ChatRoute
    Mood --> MoodRoute
    Journal --> JournalRoute
    Profile --> ProfileRoute
    
    API --> Utils
    ChatRoute --> AI
    Utils --> DB
```

---

## User Authentication Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Start([User Opens App]) --> Landing[index.html - Landing Page]
    Landing --> Choice{Choose Auth Method}
    
    Choice --> |Regular Signup| Signup[Fill Signup Form]
    Choice --> |Login| Login[Fill Login Form]
    Choice --> |Anonymous| Anon[Fill Anonymous Form]
    
    Signup --> |POST /api/auth/signup| ValidateSignup{Validate Input}
    ValidateSignup --> |Invalid| ErrorSignup[Show Error]
    ErrorSignup --> Signup
    ValidateSignup --> |Valid| CheckEmail{Email Exists?}
    CheckEmail --> |Yes| EmailError[Email Already Registered]
    EmailError --> Signup
    CheckEmail --> |No| CreateUser[Create User in DB]
    
    Login --> |POST /api/auth/login| ValidateLogin{Validate Credentials}
    ValidateLogin --> |Invalid| ErrorLogin[Show Error]
    ErrorLogin --> Login
    ValidateLogin --> |Valid| FindUser{Find User}
    FindUser --> |Not Found| UserNotFound[Invalid Credentials]
    UserNotFound --> Login
    FindUser --> |Found| CheckPass{Password Match?}
    CheckPass --> |No| PassError[Invalid Credentials]
    PassError --> Login
    CheckPass --> |Yes| SessionCreate[Create Session]
    
    Anon --> |POST /api/auth/anonymous| ValidateAnon{Validate Username}
    ValidateAnon --> |Taken| SuggestName[Suggest Alternative]
    SuggestName --> Anon
    ValidateAnon --> |Available| CreateAnon[Create Anonymous User]
    
    CreateUser --> SessionCreate
    CreateAnon --> SessionCreate
    
    SessionCreate --> StoreLocal[Store User in localStorage]
    StoreLocal --> Redirect[Redirect to chat.html]
    Redirect --> ChatPage([Chat Interface])
```

---

## Main Chat Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    subgraph Init["🚀 Initialization"]
        ChatLoad([chat.html Loads]) --> CheckAuth{User Logged In?}
        CheckAuth --> |No| RedirectLogin[Redirect to index.html]
        CheckAuth --> |Yes| LoadUI[Initialize UI Components]
        LoadUI --> LoadHistory[Load Chat History]
        LoadHistory --> LoadMood[Load Mood Data]
        LoadMood --> LoadJournal[Load Recent Journals]
        LoadJournal --> Ready([Chat Ready])
    end
    
    subgraph ChatProcess["💬 Chat Process"]
        Ready --> UserInput[User Types Message]
        UserInput --> SendBtn[Click Send / Enter]
        SendBtn --> |POST /api/chat| ProcessMsg{Process Message}
        
        ProcessMsg --> CrisisCheck{Crisis Detection}
        CrisisCheck --> |Crisis Keywords Found| CrisisPrompt[Use CRISIS_SYSTEM_PROMPT]
        CrisisCheck --> |Normal Message| NormalPrompt[Use NORMAL_SYSTEM_PROMPT]
        
        CrisisPrompt --> GetContext[Fetch User Context]
        NormalPrompt --> GetContext
        
        GetContext --> BuildContext[Build Context String]
        BuildContext --> FetchMood[Get Latest Mood]
        FetchMood --> FetchJournals[Get Last 5 Journals]
        FetchJournals --> PreparePayload[Prepare AI Request]
        
        PreparePayload --> CallAI[Call Heroku Inference API]
        CallAI --> StreamResponse[Stream SSE Response]
        StreamResponse --> RenderChunks[Render Chunks in UI]
        RenderChunks --> Complete[Complete Response]
        Complete --> SaveSession[Save to Chat History]
        SaveSession --> CheckCrisis{Crisis Detected?}
        CheckCrisis --> |Yes| ShowModal[Show Emergency Modal]
        CheckCrisis --> |No| UserInput
        ShowModal --> UserChoice{User Choice}
        UserChoice --> |Call 119| EmergencyCall[Open Phone Dialer]
        UserChoice --> |Continue Chat| UserInput
    end
```

---

## AI Response Generation Flow

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    subgraph Input["📥 Input Processing"]
        Msg[User Message] --> Crisis{Crisis Check}
        Crisis --> |Yes| CrisisMode[Crisis Mode]
        Crisis --> |No| NormalMode[Normal Mode]
    end
    
    subgraph Context["📊 Context Building"]
        CrisisMode --> FetchData
        NormalMode --> FetchData
        FetchData[getDataContext] --> MoodData[Latest Mood + Note]
        FetchData --> JournalData[Last 5 Journal Entries]
        MoodData --> ContextStr[Build Context String]
        JournalData --> ContextStr
    end
    
    subgraph API["🤖 AI API Call"]
        ContextStr --> Payload[Build API Payload]
        Payload --> |System Prompt| SP[Selected System Prompt]
        Payload --> |History| Hist[Conversation History]
        Payload --> |User Message| UMsg[Current Message]
        SP --> HerokuAPI[Heroku Inference API]
        Hist --> HerokuAPI
        UMsg --> HerokuAPI
    end
    
    subgraph Output["📤 Response Streaming"]
        HerokuAPI --> SSE[Server-Sent Events]
        SSE --> Chunks[Response Chunks]
        Chunks --> Render[Real-time UI Render]
        Render --> Done([Complete])
    end
```

---

## Mood Tracker Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Start([Open Mood Tracker]) --> LoadHistory[GET /api/mood/history]
    LoadHistory --> RenderChart[Render 7-Day Chart]
    RenderChart --> ShowUI[Display Mood Interface]
    
    ShowUI --> UserAction{User Action}
    
    UserAction --> |Log Mood| SelectMood[Select Emoji 1-5]
    SelectMood --> AddNote{Add Note?}
    AddNote --> |Yes| WriteNote[Write Optional Note]
    AddNote --> |No| SaveMood
    WriteNote --> SaveMood[POST /api/mood/log]
    SaveMood --> UpdateDB[(Save to MySQL)]
    UpdateDB --> UpdateStreak[Update User Streak]
    UpdateStreak --> RefreshChart[Refresh Mood Chart]
    RefreshChart --> ShowUI
    
    UserAction --> |View Summary| CalcSummary[Calculate Weekly Average]
    CalcSummary --> ShowInsight[Display AI-Generated Insight]
    ShowInsight --> ShowUI
```

---

## Journal Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Start([Open Journal]) --> LoadEntries[GET /api/journal/entries]
    LoadEntries --> RenderList[Display Journal List]
    RenderList --> ShowDashboard[Show Journal Dashboard]
    
    ShowDashboard --> UserAction{User Action}
    
    UserAction --> |New Entry| OpenEditor[Open Write Modal]
    OpenEditor --> WriteContent[Write Journal Content]
    WriteContent --> SaveEntry[POST /api/journal/create]
    SaveEntry --> GenerateFeedback[AI Generates Feedback]
    GenerateFeedback --> StoreDB[(Save Entry + Feedback)]
    StoreDB --> RefreshList[Refresh Entry List]
    RefreshList --> ShowDashboard
    
    UserAction --> |View Entry| SelectEntry[Click Entry]
    SelectEntry --> DisplayContent[Show Full Content]
    DisplayContent --> ShowDashboard
    
    UserAction --> |Edit Entry| EditMode[Enable Edit Mode]
    EditMode --> ModifyContent[Modify Content]
    ModifyContent --> UpdateEntry[POST /api/journal/update]
    UpdateEntry --> RegenerateFeedback[Regenerate AI Feedback]
    RegenerateFeedback --> UpdateDB[(Update in MySQL)]
    UpdateDB --> RefreshList
    
    UserAction --> |Delete Entry| ConfirmDelete{Confirm?}
    ConfirmDelete --> |Yes| DeleteEntry[POST /api/journal/delete]
    DeleteEntry --> RemoveDB[(Remove from MySQL)]
    RemoveDB --> RefreshList
    ConfirmDelete --> |No| ShowDashboard
```

---

## Breathing Exercise Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Start([Open Breathing Exercise]) --> ShowUI[Display Breathing Interface]
    ShowUI --> UserStart[User Clicks Start]
    
    UserStart --> Cycle{4-7-8 Breathing Cycle}
    
    Cycle --> Inhale[Inhale - 4 Seconds]
    Inhale --> |Animation: Circle Expands| InhaleAnim[Visual Feedback]
    InhaleAnim --> Hold[Hold - 7 Seconds]
    Hold --> |Animation: Circle Holds| HoldAnim[Visual Feedback]
    HoldAnim --> Exhale[Exhale - 8 Seconds]
    Exhale --> |Animation: Circle Contracts| ExhaleAnim[Visual Feedback]
    ExhaleAnim --> CycleCount{Cycle Complete?}
    
    CycleCount --> |More Cycles| Cycle
    CycleCount --> |All Done| Complete[Exercise Complete]
    Complete --> Feedback[Show Completion Message]
    Feedback --> ShowUI
```

---

## Profile Management Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Start([Open Profile Page]) --> CheckAuth{Authenticated?}
    CheckAuth --> |No| RedirectLogin[Redirect to Login]
    CheckAuth --> |Yes| LoadProfile[GET /api/profile]
    
    LoadProfile --> DisplayInfo[Show User Information]
    DisplayInfo --> ShowStats[Display Stats & Streaks]
    ShowStats --> ShowUI[Profile Dashboard]
    
    ShowUI --> UserAction{User Action}
    
    UserAction --> |Edit Nickname| OpenEdit[Enable Edit Mode]
    OpenEdit --> TypeName[Enter New Nickname]
    TypeName --> SaveName[PUT /api/profile/update]
    SaveName --> UpdateDB[(Update in MySQL)]
    UpdateDB --> RefreshUI[Refresh Profile Display]
    RefreshUI --> ShowUI
    
    UserAction --> |View Stats| ShowDetailed[Detailed Statistics]
    ShowDetailed --> MoodStats[Mood Tracking Stats]
    MoodStats --> JournalStats[Journal Entry Count]
    JournalStats --> StreakInfo[Current Streak]
    StreakInfo --> ShowUI
    
    UserAction --> |Logout| ClearSession[Clear localStorage]
    ClearSession --> RedirectLogin
```

---

## Database Schema

```mermaid
erDiagram
    USERS {
        varchar id PK
        varchar fullName
        varchar email UK
        varchar username UK
        varchar password
        datetime joinedDate
        boolean isAnonymous
        int streak
        date lastActiveDate
    }
    
    CHATS {
        varchar id PK
        varchar userId FK
        varchar title
        json messages
        datetime createdAt
        datetime updatedAt
    }
    
    MOOD_LOGS {
        int id PK
        varchar userId FK
        int moodLevel
        text note
        datetime loggedAt
    }
    
    JOURNAL_ENTRIES {
        int id PK
        varchar userId FK
        text content
        text aiFeedback
        datetime createdAt
        datetime updatedAt
    }
    
    USERS ||--o{ CHATS : "has"
    USERS ||--o{ MOOD_LOGS : "logs"
    USERS ||--o{ JOURNAL_ENTRIES : "writes"
```

---

## Complete System Flow Summary

```mermaid
flowchart TB
    User([👤 User]) --> |Opens App| Landing[🏠 Landing Page]
    
    Landing --> Auth{🔐 Authentication}
    Auth --> |Success| ChatUI[💬 Chat Interface]
    
    ChatUI --> Features{Select Feature}
    
    Features --> |Chat| AIChat[🤖 AI Counselor]
    Features --> |Mood| MoodTracker[📊 Mood Tracker]
    Features --> |Journal| JournalModule[📓 Journal]
    Features --> |Breathing| BreathingExercise[🧘 Breathing]
    Features --> |Profile| ProfilePage[👤 Profile]
    
    AIChat --> |Message| ProcessAI{Process}
    ProcessAI --> |Normal| NormalResponse[😊 Empathetic Response]
    ProcessAI --> |Crisis| CrisisResponse[🚨 Crisis Support]
    CrisisResponse --> |Hotline| Emergency[📞 119 Hotline]
    
    MoodTracker --> |Log| MoodDB[(💾 Save Mood)]
    JournalModule --> |Write| JournalDB[(💾 Save Entry)]
    
    MoodDB --> AIContext[📊 AI Context]
    JournalDB --> AIContext
    AIContext --> AIChat
    
    ProfilePage --> Settings[⚙️ Manage Account]
    Settings --> |Logout| Landing
```

